data.description: Great condo in quiet neighborhood. Conveniently close to the Clearfield Front Runner Station, HAFB, quick I-15 access, grocery shopping, schools, Clearfield Aquatic Center, and 30 minutes from Salt Lake. Seller has done nice upgrades, refrigerator, washer and dryer included as well as the brand new dishwasher! Unit includes one covered parking space.
